    %h2 Basics of Promotion
    %p
      Androcommerce freemium is a great tool to lift you of the ground. Your ecommerce start-up will get serious boost with personal Android storefront app. The app will be located at dedicated page of Androcommerce Market - a portal similar to Google's Play Market.
      %br
      Your storefront app will have dedicated web link for direct download. Further, each product placed by you at your storefront will be accessible via dedicated page under Androcommerce Market portal.
      %br
      %a{:name => 'inbound_marketing'}
      So nothing stops you from promoting both your storefront app and your products using Twitter, Facebook, G+ or any other social platform, whatever tickles your fancy. There is no cost to it, so feel free to form a group of enthusiasts around your store-front and then be in touch with your followers.
      

.row
